    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>file-overlap with ActionEndpoints.cs from task 040 — both tasks edit the same file. Task 044 adds rate-limit policy configuration + per-endpoint binding. Sequential after 040 lands; can run in parallel-after-040 with task 045 ONLY if both tasks coordinate the same-file edits via separate commits (conservative: mark as sequential).</parallel-reason>
